ORIGINAL MAP FROM mortis1966

Quote from mortis1966:

This is the last version of fubar towers that i will be doing (and my best i think)
50 spawn points for larger servers
texture changes make it look better than earlier versions
more teleporters and some teleport destination changes all hidden
some new hidden ladders for better access
rooms that where easy to defend as humans may not be as easy to defend as there are sneaky ways in if you can find them
a new platform under the top room of the small tower with 2 ways to access
and as requested a hidden party room with flashing lights and music, 2 ways to access one sliding door no so hard to find, one teleporter hard to find and one teleport out hard to find
i tried to make this map as fair as i could for humans and zombies
download and have fun
